heading: Vault of The Forsaken Dungeon Guide
content: Vault of The Forsaken is a slow and dreadful dungeon with a Slay all objective, a winding and confusing design, and a slow boss. The Codex of Power here isn't good either, the . Maybe save this one for last if you're going for 100% completion or Renown farming. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
